&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>On my development server, it outputs &lt;code>Sun Oct 18 18:01:01 CST 2020&lt;/code>, but in docker, it print a UTC time.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>